http://www.sohu.com/a/437504706_102080	58678
<p>大家有没有刷抖音呀？</p>
<p>大人这两天一刷抖音，十个关晓彤排队蹦出来，让我买奶茶。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201211/4be605c8eb464dadbc43afef4520908d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>原来是关晓彤在成都的奶茶店开业了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201211/aad29e59305d461e8172b2dddfd20ef2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>还请了好多网红来做推广。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201211/3ad55fe3f07447ceb247c0f6f76bd9ab.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
